{"tid":552885,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"料連續9日跌破10℃　半世紀首次","createTime":"2018-02-07T03:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T15:36:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"63a1e811508730ff8d51447ca8f4c03858bcb551","tid":552885,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180207/20297808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F20297808&d=gcwCLdnYsGG3nWdkoZNjkAHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=2b00ebb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F20297808&h=5a14fe10\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180207/20297808</a><br />\n<br />\n料連續9日跌破10℃　半世紀首次<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】今年寒冬好像沒完沒了，天文台預計，今次寒流會持續至明天，或歷時11日才止步。民間氣象組織「地下天文台」翻查天文台過往連續每日低溫少於10℃的紀錄，最長的一次是1900年，歷時12日；其次是1968年的最長寒潮，當中持續每日低溫少於10℃的日數，維持11日。若今次寒潮令市區連續9日錄得單位數氣溫，則是有紀錄以來第4長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180207/large/0205yee3002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180207%2Flarge%2F0205yee3002.jpg&h=2681c7d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n若今次寒潮令市區連續9日錄得單位數氣溫，則是有紀錄以來第4長。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反氣旋令冷空氣擴展<br />\n<br />\n本港歷來最長寒潮是在1968年，當時市區連續27日的低溫均在12℃或以下；其次是2008年，該次寒流也持續24日。<br />\n<br />\n相比之下，若今次寒潮只歷時11日，其實十大不入，不算特別長。但以市區連續每日錄得單位數氣溫計算，今次寒潮若如天文台所料，市區連續9日均低於10℃，將是1968年以來首次。<br />\n<br />\n天文台科學主任梁恩瑜以「點解凍咗咁多日？」為題撰文解釋，指出因高緯度地區上空有移動緩慢的反氣旋形成，阻塞氣流，有利內陸的冷空氣頻密由北向南擴展；季候風的補充過去幾日分批抵達華南，不斷將北面的寒冷空氣帶到沿岸，其間本港大致多雲，初時更有幾陣雨，缺乏太陽照耀，令日間氣溫仍徘徊寒冷水平。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李鈺廷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t氣溫過山車　年三十回升至20℃<br />\n港聞 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t北區-0.6℃　打鼓嶺菜田結霜<br />\n港聞 4小時前"},{"pid":"038ba91d9bc95a631d75e6d9eb49df4e4174290e","tid":552885,"uid":134487,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:21:10.000Z","msg":"極端天氣"},{"pid":"f051779db0a319445422ef5cf72765b73c981540","tid":552885,"uid":103930,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:22:19.000Z","msg":"淨係覺得條女幾正"},{"pid":"99f0ac371d64030db07dd2421cf8a6e398a63635","tid":552885,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f051779db0a319445422ef5cf72765b73c981540","tid":552885,"uid":103930,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:22:19.000Z","msg":"淨係覺得條女幾正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:32:38.000Z","msg":"當毒果影女 流架"},{"pid":"dc65d0d41e94f505e9d1e5f6d089b7dab51b7c5b","tid":552885,"uid":4179,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:36:40.000Z","msg":"暖化撚有咩好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d839a9097c8f5a099cbb016030e5ebc5e1abb9ae","tid":552885,"uid":21392,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"凍個幾日就阿支阿左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁先係冬天囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1079d83f3de3a48123895f437d44f845522c318c","tid":552885,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f051779db0a319445422ef5cf72765b73c981540","tid":552885,"uid":103930,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:22:19.000Z","msg":"淨係覺得條女幾正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:40:55.000Z","msg":"大陸妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b684b10a9d138162ea267b6dfcb2a2b73469b31a","tid":552885,"uid":128014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d839a9097c8f5a099cbb016030e5ebc5e1abb9ae","tid":552885,"uid":21392,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"凍個幾日就阿支阿左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cl